The Spending Data Pipeline
-------------------------

.. raw:: html

In this course, we will take you through the steps involved in visualising budget and spending information to make it easy to understand. In the process, you'll learn how to wrangle and clean up some of the most common errors which we see in spending and budget data, as well as doing some dataset gymnastics, such as transposition and cleanup.

