    <div class="caption offset2">
             <h3>Extracting Data From PDFs</h3>
             <p>The formats in which budgets and spending data are often release are often non-machine-readable. Any kind of profound analysis, data manipulation or visualisation is going to require data in a machine-readable format. We'll show you some of the choices involved in deciding which option to use when liberating data from PDFs.</p>
