                    <h3>Extracting Data From Websites</h3>
                    <p>The formats in which budgets and spending data are often release are often non-machine-readable. Scraping is a technique which allows you to extract information from websites without the painful copy-paste trauma! And, contrary to popular opinion, for simple websites, you don't even need to code! </p>
